<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Organization Deleted</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f7; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f4f7; padding: 40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 32px 40px 0 40px;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a;">
                Rooli
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px 32px 40px;">
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a;">
                The {{orgName}} organization has been deleted
              </h2>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
                Hi {{userName}},
              </p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
                We're writing to let you know that <strong>{{orgName}}</strong> has been deleted by its owner. Your membership in this organization has been removed, along with access to its workspaces, content, and connected accounts.
              </p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
                If you believe this was a mistake, please reach out to the organization's owner directly &mdash; we're unable to restore organizations on a member's request.
              </p>

              <!-- Info box -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0; background-color: #f8f9fb; border-left: 3px solid #4f46e5; border-radius: 4px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 16px 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a;">
                      What happens next?
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;">
                      You can continue using Rooli with any other organizations you're a member of, or create a new one of your own.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- CTA button -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="border-radius: 6px; background-color: #4f46e5;">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
                      Go to Dashboard
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #777;">
                Thanks for being part of Rooli.<br>
                &mdash; The Rooli Team
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px; background-color: #fafafa; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #999; text-align: center;">
                You're receiving this email because you were a member of {{orgName}} on Rooli.<br>
                &copy; {{year}} Rooli. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>